{"tid":2375850,"cid":26,"subCid":0,"title":"Game Maker Studio 被 Opera 收購","createTime":"2021-01-22T10:35:39.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-22T12:47:37.000Z","uid":249170,"like":7,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"4806e88400305305db1d470a28bacf54714e8710","tid":2375850,"uid":249170,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-22T10:35:39.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=i34WxuFVveI\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3Di34WxuFVveI&d=CT6PJiTX903K6YLxhzu4TWWjTds15DFTxBM9bbMqy3g%3D&h=cd14bbd3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=i34WxuFVveI</a><br />\n<br />\n尋日既事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />本毒on9今日先知<br />\n小弟有一段時間都係用Game Maker Studio 2 寫Game<br />\n不過近排轉用左Godot<br />\n<br />\n今日發現佢比瀏覽器業者Opera收購，而<span class=\"x-large\">Opera 早前已經比支那收購左</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n即係YoYo Games的遊戲開發平台GameMaker已經係支那野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有d痛心，話哂都係本人EX, 依家竟然落左去支那手上<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔知已買左既license 會唔會失效<br />\n<br />\nGMS2整2D game無疑係比Unity優秀<br />\n但Godot既出現，顯得GMS2 d缺點更明顯<br />\n<br />\n-Game Maker 整唔到3D Game（只能整假3D）<br />\n-唔支援物理效果，寫Mario 橫向遊戲，個player 唔能夠企係斜向平台，要另外Hard Code<br />\n-Template要比錢買<br />\n-多平台輸出要比錢買<br />\n<span class=\"x-large\">係超大既敗筆位</span><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"x-large\">GMS2上很多功能都得自己寫，但Godot相應的功能早已經已經內置好</span><br />\n<br />\nGodot 易用，輕量，多平台導出，而且全部免費，又易用過gamemaker千萬倍<br />\n用Godot開發既game 同GMS2不相伯仲<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n唔少外國遊戲開發者都由Game Maker Studio 2轉用Godot<br />\nHeartBeast 係其中一個<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n以下為轉貼<br />\n瀏覽器業者Opera在20日宣布，已買下英國遊戲開發商YoYo Games，亦結合與YoYo Games的遊戲開發平台GameMakerOpera GX遊戲瀏覽器，成立全新的Opera Gaming遊戲部門。<br />\n<br />\nYoYo Games最知名的產品為GameMaker Studio 2遊戲建置平台，標榜不管是專家或學生都能透過該平台打造自己的2D遊戲，還能同時匯出到不同的平台上，涵蓋遊戲機、桌面、行動及網頁。<br />\n<br />\n至於Opera GX則是Opera專為遊戲所開發的瀏覽器，它除了具備標準的Opera瀏覽器功能之外，還包含許多針對遊戲量身打造的功能，像是快速登入Twitch、調整瀏覽器所使用的系統資源比例、呈現各種遊戲資訊的GX corner，還允許使用者於側欄中加入 Facebook Messenger與Telegram等即時通訊程式，已於去年10月開放早期存取測試。<br />\n<br />\nOpera執行副總裁Krystian Kolondra表示，併購YoYo Games將替開發人員與教育工作者帶來許多可能性，Opera將會繼續發展Opera GX並推動GameMaker的成長，使GameMaker更容易讓初學者上手，同時成為商業遊戲工作室的主要2D遊戲引擎。"},{"pid":"aecbb27631f13cdaec76db54fdfa6bb9390bfbfc","tid":2375850,"uid":249170,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-22T11:03:55.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://udn.com/news/story/7086/5194204\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fudn.com%2Fnews%2Fstory%2F7086%2F5194204&d=CT6PJiTX903K6YLxhzu4TWWjTds15DFTxBM9bbMqy3g%3D&h=42acf595\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://udn.com/news/story/7086/5194204</a>"},{"pid":"dc46946bf513f4f487178ba55542c615f5edef43","tid":2375850,"uid":13879,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-22T11:55:56.000Z","msg":"巴打有咩game"},{"pid":"1f3d4cca3a684481c4ba61063fa1cd6c2ca7cada","tid":2375850,"uid":249170,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"dc46946bf513f4f487178ba55542c615f5edef43","tid":2375850,"uid":13879,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-22T11:55:56.000Z","msg":"巴打有咩game"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-22T12:19:12.000Z","msg":"之前都係寫 賭博遊戲 同埋 E-learning 既益智遊戲多<br />\n<br />\n依家都係 整緊隻屬於自己既Game<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n同係星期六，日 或者 係公司偷偷地寫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n希望有生之年出到隻game"},{"pid":"e93533602a270bd31d93a5235334319085736470","tid":2375850,"uid":13879,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1f3d4cca3a684481c4ba61063fa1cd6c2ca7cada","tid":2375850,"uid":249170,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":